### Login as Admin
POST http://localhost:5001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Username": "admin",
  "Password": "adminpass"
}

###

### Login as User
POST http://localhost:5001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Username": "user",
  "Password": "userpass"
}

###

### Login with Invalid Credentials
POST http://localhost:5001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Username": "invalid",
  "Password": "wrong"
}

###

### Get Current User Info (requires token from login)
# First login as admin or user, copy the token, then use it below
GET http://localhost:5001/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Test Admin-Only Endpoint - Get All Users (requires admin token)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/users/all?page=0
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Test Admin-Only Endpoint with User Token (should return 403)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/users/all?page=0
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_USER_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Test Protected Endpoint Without Token (should return 401)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/users/all?page=0

